HEADWORD: Deprostrate
<hw>De*pros"trate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Fully prostrate;
humble; low; rude.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>How may weak mortal ever hope to file⟦br⟧
His unsmooth tongue, and his <qex>deprostrate</qex> style.</q>
<rj><qau>G. Fletcher.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Deprovincialize</ent>⟦br⟧
